snippet.textDisplay:
I wonder what happened to AC Milan.. I haven't followed the Serie A for a long time, and now I'm supprised that AC Milan is a mid table team. I remember back in the 90's - 2000's AC Milan was among the greatest clubs in the world(not only one of the best in Europe, but also one of the best in the world).

There are so many legends from AC Milan. I wonder what really happened?? is director Galliani still with Milan??
